title: NewAir AB-850 Beverage Cooler Video Tour
description:
Get an inside look at the AB-850 Beverage Cooler from NewAir. This can beverage cooler is compact enough to fit on counters, beside a recliner in the game room, or anywhere you want easy access to your favorite drinks. You can cool up to 84 standard size cans of beer and soda, and the metal racks inside are removable for added versatility.

As you'll see in the video, features like customizable temperature control, blue interior LED lighting, and an elegant glass door harmonize in the NewAir AB-850 to create a one-of-a-kind drink fridge. With a one year warranty and a commitment to outstanding customer service from NewAir, you can rely on this appliance to keep your brews chilled and within reach for years to come.
